<HEADLINE> Seychelles Party Congratulates Jiang on Re-election </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 23 (Xinhua) -- Danny Faure, principal
executive coordinator of Seychelles People's Progressive
Front (SPPF), the ruling party of the Indian Ocean island country,
has congratulated Jiang Zemin on his re-election as general
secretary of the Central Committee of the Communist Party of China
(CPC).
</P>
<P>
"The Seychelles People's Progressive Front Central Committee
was happy to learn that Comrade Jiang Zemin was elected as General
Secretary at the First Plenary Session of the 15th Central
Committee of the CPC on September 19," said Faure in a message
sent on Monday.
</P>
<P>
Faure also expressed his hope for continued friendship and
solidarity with the CPC and wished the people of China progress
and happiness. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
