continue on its efforts aimed at achieving a negotiated peaceful
settlement to the crisis in Burundi.
</P>
<P>
The Ethiopian government supports attempts made by the
Burundian government to negotiate with various political
orgaizations with a view to peacefully resolve the crisis in
Burundi, he added.
</P>
<P>
The Burundian ambassador expressed appreciation to Ethiopia's
efforts geared towards seeking peaceful solution to the crisis in
that country, according to the report. 
