of China that ended last week was an historical meeting with a
significance that spans two centuries, establishing Deng Xiaoping
Theory as the guiding ideology of the CPC. It also elected a new
CPC leadership with Jiang Zemin at the core.
</P>
<P>
He said that China's armed forces are determined to hold high
the great banner of Deng Xiaoping Theory and to unite more closely
around the CPC Central Committee with Jiang Zemin at the core, to
devote themselves to pushing the cause of building socialism with
Chinese characteristics into the 21st century.
</P>
<P>
Pereira said that Brazil followed with great interest the 15th
Party National Congress which defined the direction of China's
development. 
</P>
