raising people's living standards and improving human rights as
well and great achievements have been made so far. However, Qian
said, the country is still faced with an arduous task for greater
progress.
</P>
<P>
China attaches importance to cooperation with the United
Nations in the field of human rights, he said.
</P>
<P>
There are great disparities in the actual conditions of
different countries and the High Commissioner for Human Rights can
play a role in this area, the Chinese minister said.
</P>
<P>
The High Commissioner said that she would take an impartial
attitude while carrying out wide-range contacts with U.N. member
countries, helping bridge the gaps among different countries.
</P>
