<HEADLINE> Toronto Doctor Shot Dead by Patient </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
OTTAWA, September 23 (Xinhua) -- A doctor was shot and a
suspected gunman died in a medical building in suburban Toronto
this afternoon, local reports said.
</P>
<P>
"It would appear one is a doctor and one is either a patient or
an ex-patient," police said.
</P>
<P>
No other injuries was reported at the building.
</P>
<P>
The doctor was shot three times, said a witness who was at the
building when the shooting happened.
</P>
<P>
The building has been sealed off by police. 
</P>
